name: Busy Seas
description:
Controls: Arrow Keys to Move!

Stay in the dark waters to catch fish, avoid other boats and Pirates! You have 60 seconds to catch as much as possible. Good Luck!

Made in Godot 3.4 for the Godot Wild Jam 41.

Theme : Ocean

Wildcards Used: 

- Fishy Business : Include Fishing Minigame

- Sound of y'all : All  sounds in game are made with your mouth(s)
